    "This might be because the Pile dataset (Gao et al., 2021), which is known to be used as training data for GPT models, includes diverse data sources including books and web text.",
    "We also saw that adding gold salient entities to CTRLSum methods is especially beneficial for genres like voyage and wikihow.",
    "However, we did not see the power of adding gold salient entities for voyage and wikihow in GPT methods.",
    "Without adding gold entities, CTRL0 and CTRLPred models often produce summaries that are too short and abstractive, leaving out important details.",
    "By contrast, GPT summaries in all three settings are rather similar in terms of the mentioned entities."
